'''Neocomora''' was the name of sacred vaults in the city of [[Kamarkiia]] on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]]. Neocomora contained numerous ancient religious texts sacred to the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] people.<ref name="SWAJ10:WBC">{{JournalCite|10|Wanted by Cracken (Star Wars Adventure Journal)}}</ref>

During the initial [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] occupation when Kamarkiia was abandoned, Neocomora was thought destroyed until it was found by the [[Gran/Legends|Gran]] thief [[Kea Ra-Lan]], who then stole the entire contents of the vaults.<ref name="SWAJ10:WBC" />

A massive hunt was launched by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] to locate Kea Ra-Lan and retrieve the stolen texts at the behest of Wookiee representatives.<ref name="SWAJ10:WBC" />

